<HEADLINE>
FT  27 JUL 92 / Survey of New Zealand (15): Key Facts
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
 --------------------------------------------------------------------
                           KEY FACTS
 --------------------------------------------------------------------
Area                                                267,844 sq km
Population                                           3.35 million
Head of State                                  Queen Elizabeth II
